      "id": "PopularPost376472",
      "post_content": "The problem with this card is that you can't always afford to take 4 damage. Yes, it doesn't matter how little life you have as long as you win, but this card will have a hard time making you win. It's not like you're opponent is just going to sit around and let you burn them to death. I'd much rather use something like [Rift Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rift Bolt), [Incinerate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Incinerate), [Searing Spear](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Searing Spear) or even [Volcanic Hammer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Hammer). ",
      "posted_by": "OlvynChuru",
